Packages that use org.flemil.ui.component
org.flemil.control This package contains classes that play a role in the control of the application as a whole. 
org.flemil.event This package contains interfaces which should be implemented by classes that wisth to be notified when selected events occur on the items for which they are registered. 
org.flemil.ui This package contains interfaces that represent the collective properties for components that can be displayed on the screen. 
org.flemil.ui.component This package contains the actual implementation of items that can be shown on a display.
